<% provide(:page_title, "Help") %>

<h1>Help</h1>

<p>
  This reputation system web site is a layer on top of the Ruby on Rails
  Tutorial sample application.  We'll write up some help text later, once
  we know what we're doing.
</p>

<p>
  For help on the Markdown text language we use, so that you can write
