  <a href="https://kramdown.gettalong.org/quickref.html">kramdown quick
  reference</a> page.
</p>

<p>
  Get help on debugging this sample web application at the
  <a href="https://www.railstutorial.org/help">Rails Tutorial Help</a> page.
  See the <a href="https://www.railstutorial.org/book"><em>Ruby on Rails
  Tutorial</em> book</a> to learn how to program well enough to write this
  application.
</p>

<% if Rails.env.development? %>
  <h2 style="clear: both">Debugging - Your Web Page Request Environment</h2>

  <table class="table-striped">
    <% request.env.each do | key, item |
      value = item.inspect
      if value.length > 65
        value = value.slice(0, 65) + "... and #{value.length} more letters."
      end %>
      <tr><td><%= key %></td><td><%= value %></td></tr>
    <% end %>
  </table>
<% end %>

